data.description: Charming single family home in Prescott Valley, AZ! This beautifully decorated 1 level home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 1359 sq ft of living space. Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting layout with ample natural light. The open kitchen features modern appliances and plenty of cabinet space. Gas range.  Owned RO system. Eat in kitchen, Extra shelving in laundry and bedroom 2 closet. Enjoy the convenience of a primary bedroom with an attached bath. Walk in closet Attached oversized 2 car garage with direct entry. Outside, the backyard is a true oasis, showcasing lovely rose and vegatable gardens. Mountain views. This property offers both comfort and style in a desirable locaton. Don't miss out of this wonderful opportunity!
